{"type":"message","id":"eb685f48","parentId":"f0f99203","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:14:25.783Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's the contents of your OpenClaw configuration file. You can see the changes we made earlier:\n\n1. The Feishu channel is configured under a separate account with ID \"demo\" in the `channels.feishu.accounts.demo` section\n2. The binding has been updated to match the agent \"demo\" with the Feishu channel using account ID \"demo\"\n\nThe configuration is working correctly, which is why we're able to communicate through Feishu right now."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"anthropic/claude-3.7-sonnet","usage":{"input":1774,"output":110,"cacheRead":18756,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20640,"cost":{"input":0.005322,"output":0.00165,"cacheRead":0.0056267999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0125988}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773735261094}}
