{"type":"message","id":"079fad5e","parentId":"74219ee7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:19:50.312Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要为用户创建一个每天早上8点执行的定时任务，用于检查之前创建的两个知识库文件（关于OpenClaw的多代理系统和概述）是否有更新。如果有更新，需要同步关键内容并把更新摘要发送到群组。\n\n我需要使用OpenClaw的cron功能来设置这个定时任务。我需要:\n\n1. 确认cron功能是否可用\n2. 创建一个cron脚本来执行这个任务\n3. 设置cron任务，让它每天早上8点执行\n\n首先，让我查看一下OpenClaw中cron相关的功能和命令：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"我会帮您创建一个每天早上8点执行的定时任务，用于检查那两份OpenClaw文档资料的更新情况。\n\n首先，让我了解一下OpenClaw的cron功能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_013pfu7qszQhMKJnmYs6GLiw","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron -h"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"anthropic/claude-3.7-sonnet","usage":{"input":25952,"output":505,"cacheRead":21340,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47797,"cost":{"input":0.07785600000000001,"output":0.007575,"cacheRead":0.006402,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.09183300000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773735580827}}
{"type":"message","id":"d64fbb34","parentId":"079fad5e","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:19:56.337Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_013pfu7qszQhMKJnmYs6GLiw","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools[39m\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Open source means you can see exactly how I judge your config.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6021,"aggregated":"[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools[39m\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Open source means you can see exactly how I judge your config.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.","cwd":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773735596336}}
