{"type":"message","id":"261a7d64","parentId":"b8eb681f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:22:33.318Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01QdXqYDCzVs8qr9HcPhLDJR","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"==== OpenClaw文档更新检查 - Tue Mar 17 04:22:21 PM CST 2026 ====\n正在检查 https://docs.OpenClaw.ai/zh-CN/concepts/multi-agent 的更新...\n检测到HTML内容，尝试提取有用的Markdown部分...\n未找到特定Markdown部分，提取可读文本...\n! 发现 openclaw-multi-agent 有更新\n正在检查 https://github.com/OpenClaw/OpenClaw 的更新...\n检测到HTML内容，尝试提取有用的Markdown部分...\n未找到特定Markdown部分，提取可读文本...\n! 发现 openclaw-overview 有更新\n这是首次运行，初始化知识库文件\n知识库已初始化。下次运行将检测真实更改。"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7,"aggregated":"==== OpenClaw文档更新检查 - Tue Mar 17 04:22:21 PM CST 2026 ====\n正在检查 https://docs.OpenClaw.ai/zh-CN/concepts/multi-agent 的更新...\n检测到HTML内容，尝试提取有用的Markdown部分...\n未找到特定Markdown部分，提取可读文本...\n! 发现 openclaw-multi-agent 有更新\n正在检查 https://github.com/OpenClaw/OpenClaw 的更新...\n检测到HTML内容，尝试提取有用的Markdown部分...\n未找到特定Markdown部分，提取可读文本...\n! 发现 openclaw-overview 有更新\n这是首次运行，初始化知识库文件\n知识库已初始化。下次运行将检测真实更改。","cwd":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773735753316}}
{"type":"message","id":"97a77b6c","parentId":"261a7d64","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:23:00.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"很好，我们的脚本已经成功检测到这是首次运行，并且正确初始化了知识库文件。让我们检查一下子代理脚本，确保它能够正确处理脚本输出："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_018Cq6wKheyQL5rCbYEGL1w8","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/scripts/docs_update_agent.js","oldText":"/**\n * OpenClaw文档更新检查子代理\n * \n * 此子代理负责：\n * 1. 运行文档检查脚本\n * 2. 分析结果\n * 3. 如果有更新，格式化并发送到飞书\n */\n\n// 获取今天的日期\nconst today = new Date();\nconst dateStr = today.toISOString().split('T')[0];\n\nasync function run() {\n  // 打印任务开始信息\n  console.log(`[${dateStr}] 开始检查OpenClaw文档更新...`);\n  \n  try {\n    // 运行文档检查脚本\n    const scriptPath = '/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/scripts/check_openclaw_docs.sh';\n    const result = await exec(`bash ${scriptPath}`);\n    \n    // 检查脚本执行状态\n    if (result.exitCode === 0) {\n      console.log(\"文档检查完成：没有发现更新\");\n      return \"OpenClaw文档没有更新。\";\n    } else {\n      console.log(\"文档检查完成：发现更新！\");\n      \n      // 解析输出以提取更新摘要\n      const updateSummary = parseUpdateSummary(result.stdout);\n      \n      // 格式化飞书消息\n      const message = formatMessage(updateSummary);\n      \n      return message;\n    }\n  } catch (error) {\n    console.error(\"执行文档检查脚本时出错:\", error);\n    return `OpenClaw文档检查过程中发生错误: ${error.message}`;\n  }\n}\n\n// 解析更新摘要\nfunction parseUpdateSummary(output) {\n  // 提取更新摘要部分\n  const summaryMatch = output.match(/==== OpenClaw文档更新摘要[\\s\\S]*$/);\n  if (summaryMatch) {\n    return summaryMatch[0];\n  }\n  \n  return \"检测到更新，但无法解析具体内容。请查看日志获取详情。\";\n}\n\n// 格式化飞书消息\nfunction formatMessage(summary) {\n  return `# 📢 OpenClaw文档更新通知 (${dateStr})\n\n检测到OpenClaw文档有新的更新！以下是更新摘要：\n\n${summary}\n\n您可以通过以下命令查看完整文档：\n\\`\\`\\`\ncat /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/knowledge/openclaw-multi-agent.md\ncat /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/knowledge/openclaw-overview.md\n\\`\\`\\`\n`;\n}\n\n// 运行并返回结果\nreturn run();","newText":"/**\n * OpenClaw文档更新检查子代理\n * \n * 此子代理负责：\n * 1. 运行文档检查脚本\n * 2. 分析结果\n * 3. 如果有更新，格式化并发送到飞书\n */\n\n// 获取今天的日期\nconst today = new Date();\nconst dateStr = today.toISOString().split('T')[0];\n\nasync function run() {\n  // 打印任务开始信息\n  console.log(`[${dateStr}] 开始检查OpenClaw文档更新...`);\n  \n  try {\n    // 运行文档检查脚本\n    const scriptPath = '/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/scripts/check_openclaw_docs.sh';\n    const result = await exec(`bash ${scriptPath}`);\n    \n    // 检查脚本输出是否包含初始化信息\n    if (result.stdout && result.stdout.includes(\"初始化知识库文件\")) {\n      console.log(\"知识库初始化完成，无需发送更新通知\");\n      return \"OpenClaw文档知识库已初始化完成。将在下次运行时检测真实更新。\";\n    }\n    \n    // 检查脚本执行状态\n    if (result.exitCode === 0) {\n      console.log(\"文档检查完成：没有发现更新\");\n      return \"OpenClaw文档没有更新。\";\n    } else {\n      console.log(\"文档检查完成：发现更新！\");\n      \n      // 解析输出以提取更新摘要\n      const updateSummary = parseUpdateSummary(result.stdout);\n      \n      // 格式化飞书消息\n      const message = formatMessage(updateSummary);\n      \n      return message;\n    }\n  } catch (error) {\n    console.error(\"执行文档检查脚本时出错:\", error);\n    \n    // 检查是否是脚本不存在的错误\n    if (error.message && error.message.includes(\"No such file or directory\")) {\n      return `错误：文档检查脚本不存在，请确认路径: /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/scripts/check_openclaw_docs.sh`;\n    }\n    \n    return `OpenClaw文档检查过程中发生错误: ${error.message}`;\n  }\n}\n\n// 解析更新摘要\nfunction parseUpdateSummary(output) {\n  // 提取更新摘要部分\n  const summaryMatch = output.match(/==== OpenClaw文档更新摘要[\\s\\S]*$/);\n  if (summaryMatch) {\n    return summaryMatch[0];\n  }\n  \n  // 检查是否有日志文件信息\n  const logMatch = output.match(/生成的摘要在\\s+([^\\s]+)/);\n  if (logMatch) {\n    return `检测到更新，详细摘要保存在: ${logMatch[1]}`;\n  }\n  \n  return \"检测到文档更新，但无法解析具体内容。请查看日志获取详情。\";\n}\n\n// 格式化飞书消息\nfunction formatMessage(summary) {\n  return `# 📢 OpenClaw文档更新通知 (${dateStr})\n\n检测到OpenClaw文档有新的更新！以下是更新摘要：\n\n${summary}\n\n您可以通过以下命令查看完整文档：\n\\`\\`\\`\ncat /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/knowledge/openclaw-multi-agent.md\ncat /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/knowledge/openclaw-overview.md\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n或直接查看知识库目录：\n\\`\\`\\`\nls -l /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo/knowledge/\n\\`\\`\\`\n`;\n}\n\n// 运行并返回结果\nreturn run();"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"anthropic/claude-3.7-sonnet","usage":{"input":431,"output":1972,"cacheRead":65064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67467,"cost":{"input":0.001293,"output":0.029580000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0195192,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0503922}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773735753319}}
