{"type":"message","id":"c0664402","parentId":"392615f6","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:26:07.945Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01NdfDawdrBiWVAmug7nAopS","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools[39m\nID                                   Name                     Schedule                         Next       Last       Status    Target    Agent ID   Model               \n26e0b6a6-61e8-46a4-a7e8-4e07d977b8ba OpenClaw文档每日更新检查         cron 0 8 * * * (exact)           in 16h     -          idle      isolated  demo       -"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6424,"aggregated":"[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools[39m\nID                                   Name                     Schedule                         Next       Last       Status    Target    Agent ID   Model               \n26e0b6a6-61e8-46a4-a7e8-4e07d977b8ba OpenClaw文档每日更新检查         cron 0 8 * * * (exact)           in 16h     -          idle      isolated  demo       -","cwd":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-demo"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773735967944}}
{"type":"message","id":"f85662d0","parentId":"c0664402","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:26:16.581Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"很好，我们已经成功设置了一个每天早上8点执行的定时任务，它将：\n\n1. 运行文档检查脚本，该脚本会：\n   - 获取OpenClaw的多代理概念文档和GitHub仓库页面\n   - 与本地知识库文件比较以检查是否有更新\n   - 如果有更新，生成一个更新摘要\n\n2. 如果检测到更新，子代理脚本会：\n   - 处理更新摘要（特别是处理任何HTML内容）\n   - 格式化一个包含更新摘要的消息\n   - 发送到飞书群组\n\n该任务经过了优化，可以处理首次运行和HTML内容的情况，并提供有用的错误处理和日志记录。\n\n您可以使用以下命令测试这个任务：\n```\nopenclaw cron run 26e0b6a6-61e8-46a4-a7e8-4e07d977b8ba\n```\n\n这将立即执行任务，而不必等到早上8点。\n\n这个定时任务已经设置好了，您不需要做任何额外的事情。它将按照计划每天早上8点自动检查文档更新，并在发现更新时通知您。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"anthropic/claude-3.7-sonnet","usage":{"input":2392,"output":372,"cacheRead":137355,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140119,"cost":{"input":0.007176,"output":0.00558,"cacheRead":0.0412065,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0539625}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773735967949}}
